{"title":"青铜骑士","authors":["金哲"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青铜骑士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金哲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝重的黄昏两个人影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天地的交接处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而抖鬃嘶鸣的骏马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾跃动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的地平线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥赶起马群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥赶起连绵的峻岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦地　长焦距镜头般"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由远而近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞬间映进我睁大的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你吗　汹涌的波涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排山倒海的集团军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声惊雷滚过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡涤草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挤满偌大的天庭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳情不自禁地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用粗糙的线条雕塑出剽悍的骑士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏以古朴的色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匆匆涂抹青铜的野性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噢，粗犷的旷野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔驰高大无比的铜像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍穹无声地仰望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原呢又一次录下暴风雨骤烈的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（金学泉译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}